data.description: Gorgeous 3 Bedroom, 2 Bath Home with Upgrades! This residence boasts a thoughtfully designed split floor plan, offering privacy & functionality. A spacious living area adorned with modern finishes & abundant natural light, featuring a cozy fireplace. The heart of this home is an upgraded kitchen that revels in the granite countertops, stainless steel appliances, & ample cabinetry that provides ample storage. Enjoy quick breakfasts or host intimate dinners in the dining area. The master suite is a true retreat, offering an escape with its en-suite bath: dual vanities, and a separate shower for unwinding after a long day. Secondary bedrooms ensure plenty of space for guests or a home office. Situated just moments away from the I-45 Freeway, it's effortless commuting & quick access to neighboring cities. For a delicious meal out or a shopping spree, there are a variety of destinations less than 5 minutes away. Galveston Beach is just 35 minutes away. This is your Home Sweet Home!
